list.item:
a complete showdown on existing operations including full accounting
                            and verification of raw materials utilized to date, existing reserve and
                            pipe line stocks, nuclear fuels produced, etc.;

adequate U.N. observation over all known and declared raw material
                            sources and facilities for investigation, and if necessary, observation
                            over all alleged ones;

U.N. supervision of large reactors during deactivation or dismantling
                            stage, followed by periodic observation over sites of such
                            reactors;
